<dl id="sh.1"> <dt><a href="../../ulex/ap/sh11d.htm">sh.1</a> </dt> <dd>Fair copy (incomplete). <ul><li>MS: Harvard, Yale, Cornell 36 </li><li>Reproduced: JJA 8 1-803 </li><li>Published edition: <a href="https://archive.org/details/in.ernet.dli.2015.59181/page/n3/mode/2up" target="_blank"<cite>Stephen Hero</cite></a>, ed. Theodore Spenser, revised by John J. Slocum and Herbert Cahoon (London: Jonathan Cape, 1956). </li><li>Dates of completion of the various chapters: <br><font color="red">1902-1903</font>: The first chapters must have been written prior to Joyce's mother's death on August 13, 1903: see <a name="1Sep1916" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#1Sep1916">Letters II, 383: 1 September 1916</a>. <br><font color="red">Spring 1903Summer 1904</font>: SH IXI written: see <a name="23Jun1904" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#23Jun1904">Selected Letters, 22: 23 June 1904</a> and <a name="?15Jul1904" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#?15Jul1904">Selected Letters, 22: Friday ?15 July 1904</a>. <br><font color="red">July 1904</font>:SH XII begun:  <br><font color="red">October 1904</font>: SH XII completed:  see <a name="15Sep1904" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#15Sep1904">Letters II, 53: 15 September 1904</a> and <a name="20Oct1904" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#20Oct1904">Letters II, 67: 20 [October] 1904</a>.  <br><font color="red">Early December 1904</font>: SH XIII completed: see  <a name="3Dec1904" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#3Dec1904">Selected Letters 45-7: 3 December 1904</a> and <a name="12Dec1904" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#12Dec1904">Letters II. 74: 12 December 1904</a>.  <br><font color="red">Mid December 1904</font>: SH XIV [Mullingar episode] completed and SH XV begun: see <a name="28Dec1904" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#28Dec1904">Letters II. 75: 28 December 1904</a> and <a name="31Dec1904" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#31Dec1904">Selected Letters, 49: 31 December 1904</a>.  <br><font color="red">January 1905</font>: SH XV completed and XVI begun: see  <a name="13Jan1905" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#13Jan1905">Letters II, 76: 13 January 1905</a>.  <br><font color="red">February 1905</font>: SH XVI completed and XVII begun: see <a name="7Feb1905" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#7Feb1905">Selected Letters, 52-4: 7 February 1905</a>.  <br><font color="red">Late February 1905</font>: SH XVII completed and XVIII begun: see <a name="20Feb1905" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#20Feb1905">Letters II, 82: 20 February 1905</a>.  <br><font color="red">End of February 1905</font>: Joyce expressed dissatisfaction with the title <cite>Stephen Hero</cite>: see <a name="28Feb1905" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#28Feb1905">Selected Letters, 56: 28 February 1905</a>.  <br><font color="red">Mid-March 1905</font>: SH XVIII completed: see <a name="15Mar1905" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#15Mar1905">Selected Letters, 58: 15 March 1905</a>.  <br><font color="red">Early April 1905</font>: SH XIX and XX completed and XXI begun: see <a name="4Apr1905" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#4Apr1905">Selected Letters, 60-1: 4 April 1905</a>.  <br><font color="red">Early May 1905</font>: SH XXI completed and XXII begun: see <a name="2or3May1905" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#2or3May1905">Selected Letters, 60: 2 or 3 May 1905</a>.  <br><font color="red">May-June 1905</font>: Early chapters (SH I-XIV part 1) probably removed at this time for rewriting, and University College episode of eleven chapters (SH XIII to XXIV) not quite ready: see <a name="27May1905" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#27May1905">Letters II, 90: 27 May 1905</a>.  <br><font color="red">Early June 1905</font>: SH XXIV completed: see <a name="7Jun1905" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#7Jun1905">Letters II, 91: postmark 7 June 1905</a> and <a name="12Jul1905" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#12Jul1905">Selected Letters, 63-4: 12 July 1905</a>.  <br><font color="red">Summer 1905</font>: Sheets 903-914 of SH XXV are missing. The chapter may never have been completed. It is not clear when precisely the novel as a whole was abandoned. For later references to <cite>Stephen Hero</cite> see <a name="c24Sep1905" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#c24Sep1905">Selected Letters, 77: c. 24 September 1905</a>, <a name="3Oct1905" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#3Oct19051905">Letters II, 113-4: 3 October 1905</a>, <a name="29Oct1905" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#29Oct1905">Letters II, 125-6: 29 October 1905</a>, <a name="13Mar1906" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#13Mar1906">Letters II, 131-2: 13 March 1906</a>, <a name="6Jun1906" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#6Jun1906">Letters II, 139: 6 June 1906</a>, <a name="10Jun1906" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#10Jun1906">Letters II, 140: 10 June 1906</a>, <a name="13Oct1906" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#13Oct1906">Letters II, 179: 13 October 1906</a>, and <a name="10Jan1907" href="../ubiog/ulett.htm#10Jan1907">Selected Letters, 143: 10 January 1907</a>. </li>  <li>Notebooks used: <a name="jn0" href="../udra/unbdetails.htm#jn0">JN0 (Buffalo I.A; Cornell.18,4,17)</a>, <a name="jn1" href="../udra/unbdetails.htm#jn1">JN1 (NLI.2A)</a>, <a name="pn1" href="../udra/unbdetails.htm#pn1">PN1 (Buffalo II.A, Cornell.18,4,17)</a> </li></ul> </dd> </dl>
